    "causal_summary": "CocoIndex operators had no single preflight for three high-trust failure modes: a stale global `ccc`, non-commercial default reranker licensing, and expensive model-swap reindexing. The default reranker was empirically strong but licensed CC BY-NC 4.0, which creates silent commercial risk if the operator assumes Apache-licensed project code means unrestricted model use.",
